<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>RailConnect - Online Train Reservation</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{

background:
linear-gradient(
rgba(0,0,0,.65),
rgba(0,0,0,.65)
),

url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474487548417-781cb71495f3?w=1800");

background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
background-attachment:fixed;

color:white;
}

/* NAVBAR */

nav{

display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;

padding:20px 60px;

background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

position:sticky;
top:0;
}

.logo{

font-size:34px;
font-weight:bold;

color:#4FC3F7;
}

nav ul{

display:flex;
gap:30px;
list-style:none;
}

nav ul li{

cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

nav ul li:hover{

color:#4FC3F7;
}

.btn{

padding:12px 25px;

border:none;

border-radius:30px;

font-weight:bold;

cursor:pointer;

background:
linear-gradient(
45deg,
#4FC3F7,
#B3E5FC
);
}

/* HERO */

.hero{

height:90vh;

display:flex;
flex-direction:column;

justify-content:center;
align-items:center;

text-align:center;

padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{

font-size:78px;

margin-bottom:20px;

background:
linear-gradient(
90deg,
#fff,
#4FC3F7,
#fff
);

-webkit-background-clip:text;
-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.hero p{

font-size:22px;

max-width:850px;

color:#dff4ff;
}

/* SEARCH FORM */

.search-box{

margin-top:35px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(12px);

padding:25px;

border-radius:20px;
}

.search-box input,
.search-box select{

padding:12px;

margin:10px;

border:none;

border-radius:10px;

width:180px;
}

/* STATS */

.stats{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:25px;

padding:50px;
}

.stat-card{

width:220px;

padding:25px;

text-align:center;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

border-radius:20px;
}

.stat-card h2{

color:#4FC3F7;
}

/* SECTION TITLE */

.section-title{

text-align:center;

font-size:40px;

color:#4FC3F7;

margin:50px 0;
}

/* TRAIN CARDS */

.container{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:30px;

padding:20px 40px 60px;
}

.card{

width:300px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(15px);

border-radius:20px;

overflow:hidden;

transition:.4s;
}

.card:hover{

transform:translateY(-10px);

box-shadow:
0 15px 35px rgba(79,195,247,.3);
}

.card img{

width:100%;
height:220px;

object-fit:cover;
}

.card-content{

padding:20px;
}

.card-content h3{

color:#4FC3F7;

margin-bottom:10px;
}

.card-content p{

line-height:1.6;
}

/* PNR CHECKER */

.pnr-box{

width:600px;

margin:40px auto;

padding:30px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(12px);

border-radius:20px;

text-align:center;
}

.pnr-box input{

width:80%;

padding:12px;

border:none;

border-radius:10px;

margin-bottom:15px;
}

/* FOOTER */

footer{

text-align:center;

padding:25px;

background:rgba(0,0,0,.4);
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<nav>

<div class="logo">🚆 RailConnect</div>

<ul>

<li>Home</li>
<li>Book Ticket</li>
<li>Train Schedule</li>
<li>PNR Status</li>
<li>My Booking</li>

</ul>

<button class="btn">Login</button>

</nav>

<section class="hero">

<h1>Reserve Your Train Journey</h1>

<p>

Book train tickets, check seat availability,
track PNR status and enjoy a smooth travel experience.

</p>

<div class="search-box">

<input type="text"
placeholder="Source Station">

<input type="text"
placeholder="Destination Station">

<input type="date">

<select>

<option>Class</option>

<option>Sleeper</option>
<option>AC 3 Tier</option>
<option>AC 2 Tier</option>
<option>First Class</option>

</select>

<button class="btn">

Search Trains

</button>

</div>

</section>

<div class="stats">

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>800+</h2>
<p>Daily Trains</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>50K+</h2>
<p>Passengers</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>250+</h2>
<p>Stations</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>24/7</h2>
<p>Service</p>
</div>

</div>

<h2 class="section-title">

Train Categories

</h2>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500530855697-b586d89ba3ee?w=900">

<div class="card-content">

<h3>🚄 Vande Bharat</h3>

<p>

India's premium semi-high-speed train
with modern facilities.

</p>

</div>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474487548417-781cb71495f3?w=900">

<div class="card-content">

<h3>⚡ Superfast Express</h3>

<p>

Fast and comfortable long-distance
travel services.

</p>

</div>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517841905240-472988babdf9?w=900">

<div class="card-content">

<h3>🛏 Sleeper Class</h3>

<p>

Affordable overnight travel with
comfortable sleeping berths.

</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<h2 class="section-title">

PNR Status Checker

</h2>

<div class="pnr-box">

<input type="text"
placeholder="Enter PNR Number">

<br>

<button class="btn">

Check Status

</button>

</div>

<footer>

🚆 RailConnect Online Train Reservation System © 2026

</footer>

</body>

</html>
